Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.36,0:21:07.11,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}(Stay with you forever…)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.08,0:21:17.21,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}仿佛一望无际
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.33,0:21:24.38,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}悲伤已烟消云散
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.38,0:21:31.76,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}为了不让这份笑容黯淡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.22,0:21:39.73,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}我会一直在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.06,0:21:43.69,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}没有泪水的明天过后
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.69,0:21:47.36,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}会有温柔的未来等着你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.36,0:21:54.12,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}即便是微弱的希望 也相信着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.45,0:21:58.04,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}Reason of life一定能找到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.04,0:22:01.63,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}Feel you heart 只属于自己的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.63,0:22:06.30,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}迷茫的时候携手前行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.30,0:22:08.72,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}在现实(现在)中Survive
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.84,0:22:12.47,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}Reason of life会和你一同发现
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.47,0:22:21.44,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}生而为人的证明 与促成邂逅的点滴
Dialogue: 1,0:21:00.36,0:21:07.11,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}(Stay with you forever…)
Dialogue: 1,0:21:10.08,0:21:17.21,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}どこまでも続くような
Dialogue: 1,0:21:17.33,0:21:24.38,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}悲しみはどこにもない
Dialogue: 1,0:21:24.38,0:21:31.76,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}その笑顔 曇らないように
Dialogue: 1,0:21:32.22,0:21:39.73,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}いつでもそばにいるよ
